OL,3,CCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland announce one-day withdrawal of
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,FCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,8,FIreland have announced a one-day
OL,9,Fwithdrawal of services on November 4
OL,10,Fas part of a dispute over the payment
OL,11,Fof legal aid fees.
OL,13,FThe Criminal Bar Association (CBA)
OL,14,Fadded that from the beginning of
OL,15,FNovember, barristers will refuse
OL,16,Finstructions in all category A crown
OL,17,Fcourt cases, which include offences of
OL,18,Fmurder and manslaughter, and will also
OL,19,Frefuse instructions in any retrials in
OL,20,Frespect of all cases which follow on
OL,21,Ffrom hung juries or appeals.
