OL,7,FDonal Lunny KC, chair of the Bar of
OL,8,FNorthern Ireland, claimed the system
OL,9,Fof criminal legal aid has reached
OL,10,F"crisis point".
OL,12,FHe said: "Criminal barristers are
OL,13,Fdedicated and committed professionals,
OL,14,Fand they apply their legal knowledge
OL,15,Fto matters that are serious, complex
OL,16,Fand traumatic, providing access to
OL,17,Fjustice and ensuring a fair balance
OL,18,Fbetween the prosecution and the
OL,19,Faccused during criminal proceedings.
