OL,3,CCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland announce one-day withdrawal of
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"Criminal barristers in our crown
OL,8,Fcourts work for legal aid rates which
OL,9,Fhave, when adjusted for inflation,
OL,10,Fplummeted between 47% and 58% since
OL,11,F2005.
OL,13,F"Routinely, these barristers will wait
OL,14,Fat least three to four months for
OL,15,Fpayment once a case is concluded and
OL,16,Ftheir fee is submitted."
OL,18,FThe Department of Justice said it is
OL,19,F"surprised and disappointed that the
OL,20,FCriminal Bar Association intends to
OL,21,Ftake industrial action".
