OL,7,FIn a statement, it added: "The
OL,8,FDepartment commissioned a Fundamental
OL,9,FReview of Criminal Legal Aid which was
OL,10,Ftaken forward by HHJ Burgess and which
OL,11,Fthe Bar engaged with. The Department
OL,12,Fis considering HHJ Burgess' report and
OL,13,Fthe associated recommendations.
OL,15,F"The Department has also given
OL,16,Fundertakings to continue engaging with
OL,17,Fall stakeholders, including the Bar,
OL,18,Ffollowing a Ministerial Statement
OL,19,Fwhich will be made in the coming weeks.
