OL,3,CCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland announce one-day withdrawal of
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"It is well-known the Department of
OL,8,FJustice has been consistently
OL,9,Funderfunded and the fallout from such
OL,10,Funderfunding is now being realised.
OL,12,F"The Bar is aware that the Department
OL,13,Fhas been working to secure a more
OL,14,Fsustainable budget and additional
OL,15,Ffunding has been secured this year to
OL,16,Fmeet the current pressures.
