OL,3,CCriminal barristers in Northern
OL,4,CIreland announce one-day withdrawal of
OL,5,Cservices
OL,7,F"It should be noted that pressures
OL,8,Fwere at an all-time high in 2023/24
OL,9,Fwhen the Legal Services Agency paid
OL,10,Fout circa #114m to legal
OL,11,Fprofessionals, the highest level of
OL,12,Fpayment in the history of legal aid.
OL,14,F"The Department will continue to push
OL,15,Fhard for more funding to address the
OL,16,Funderfunding issues across Justice. It
OL,17,Fis therefore premature to announce
OL,18,Fstrike action at this time."
